docs.text: Introduction ¶ Why ¶ This website is a place for me to share things I write. I write to express and organize my thoughts and emotions. I hope these writings will be valuable to others as well. What ¶ I'm interested in writing about these types of topics: personality MBTI INFP HSP mysticism religions philosophies spirituality yoga How ¶ I am not likely to write on a regular schedule. I expect to write more when inspirations strikes.
